             was indicted for <rs id="t18231203-19-off106" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18231203-19-off106" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18231203-19-off106" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18231203-19-cd107" type="crimeDate">2d of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18231203-19-off106 t18231203-19-cd107"></join>, twelve bells, value 3 l, the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18231203-19-victim232" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Lane
                     <interp inst="t18231203-19-victim232" type="surname" value="Lane"></interp>
