                     <interp inst="t18231203-19-verdict110" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 18.</p>
               <p>Of stealing to the value of 39 s. only. <rs id="t18231203-19-punish111" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18231203-19-punish111" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
